To the Chambers of Judge Parker: 
The Government respectfully submits the attached application and proposed order for unsealing and assignment of 
United States v.  Ghisloine Maxwell, 20 Cr. 330, attached in Word and PDF formats. We would be very grateful to have the 
case unsealed as soon as practicable. 
In connection with this case, we also write to advise the Court that we expect the defendant will be presented today in 
the District of New Hampshire. 
Should there be any questions or issues, I am available anytime via phone at 
Respectfully, 
Assistant U.S. Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
EFTA00020351
